GUISTIC SUPPORT IN AUTOMATED LIBRARY SYSTEMS.AIMS TO SHOW THE CURRENT POSITION AND FUTURE DEVELOPMENT OF LINGUISTICSUPPORT, WITH PARTICULAR REFERENCE TO THE STATE AUTOMATED SYSTEM OF SCIENTIFICAND TECHNICAL INFORMATION (GASNTI). THE CONTENT AND STRUCTURE OF LINGUISTICSUPPORT IS DEFINED BY THE LEVEL OF DEVELOPMENT OF THE LIBRARY SERVICE AND THEINFORMATION INVOLVED. IN PRACTICE, LINGUISTIC SUPPORT HAS TO TAKE ACCOUNT OFNOT ONLY THE SUBJECT CONTENT BUT ALSO A RANGE OF EXTERNAL FEATURES INCLUDINGBIBLIOGRAPHICAL DESCRIPTION. ITS APPLICATION IN DIFFERENT SYSTEMS CAN BE SEENAT AN INTERNATIONAL LEVEL IN UNISIST, AS WELL AS AT NATIONAL AND LOCAL LEVEL